        what should printing the game look like? the map? map + items + monsters + player?
        should this include things like the player's health, inventory, equipped items?
    - need externally accessible getter for game state; break into separate aspects?
        dungeon map, rockmap, monster/item locations, player/player's memory, player's viewdist
